---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact — Journal Foundation"
  description="How to reach the Journal Foundation — dedicated channels for developers, advisors, funders, press, and security disclosures."
>
  <div class="container prose" style="margin-top: var(--space-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p class="lead">We’re early. If you’re a privacy-minded <strong>developer</strong>, <strong>researcher</strong>, <strong>advisor</strong>, or <strong>funder</strong> who wants to help build the post-surveillance web, we’d love to hear from you.</p>

    <h2>Primary Channels</h2>
    <ul class="channel-list">
      <li>
        <p><strong>General &amp; Partnerships —</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@journalfoundation.org" rel="nofollow">hello@journalfoundation.org</a></p>
        <p class="channel-note">Short proposals, partnership ideas, intros.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Specifications &amp; Engineering —</strong> <a href="mailto:specs@journalfoundation.org" rel="nofollow">specs@journalfoundation.org</a></p>
        <p class="channel-note">
          Protocol/RFC feedback and reference implementation questions. Please also open public threads in
            <a class="button-link" href="https://github.com/JournalFoundation/cipherlot/discussions" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Discussions →</a>
            github.com/JournalFoundation/cipherlot/discussions
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Press &amp; Speaking —</strong> <a href="mailto:press@journalfoundation.org" rel="nofollow">press@journalfoundation.org</a></p>
        <p class="channel-note">Media requests, interviews, event invitations.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Funding &amp; Grants —</strong> <a href="mailto:grants@journalfoundation.org" rel="nofollow">grants@journalfoundation.org</a></p>
        <p class="channel-note">Philanthropy, research grants, programmatic support.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Community &amp; Code</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>GitHub Discussions:</strong>
      <a class="button-link" href="https://github.com/JournalFoundation/cipherlot/discussions" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Discussions →</a>
        <span class="url-text">github.com/JournalFoundation/cipherlot/discussions</span><br />
      Best for public questions, RFC debates, and roadmap ideas.
    </p>

    <h2 id="security-disclosure">Security / Responsible Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Report vulnerabilities to <a href="mailto:security@journalfoundation.org" rel="nofollow">security@journalfoundation.org</a>. Encrypt mail with our PGP key:
    </p>
    <pre><code>Fingerprint: A1B2 C3D4 EF56 789A BCDE  F012 3456 789A BCDE F012
Key: https://journalfoundation.org/pgp/security.asc</code></pre>
    <p>We publish <strong>/.well-known/security.txt</strong> (RFC 9116) with these details.</p>

    <h2>Tips for Sensitive Outreach</h2>
    <p>
      You may use Signal: <strong>+1-000-000-0000</strong>. Signal shares your number with us; feel free to use a secondary number. We may introduce heavier-weight options (e.g., SecureDrop) as the program matures.
    </p>

    <h2>Response Policy</h2>
    <p>We triage new messages weekly. If we miss you, please nudge us or open a GitHub Discussion. Security reports are prioritized and acknowledged within <strong>72 hours</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>No forms. No trackers. Email us or open a public thread; we don’t harvest, resell, or profile your contact info.</p>

    <!-- Optional scheduling once you have a privacy-first booking flow -->
    <!-- <p><a href="https://cal.yourdomain.example/briefing">Request a briefing (privacy-friendly scheduling)</a></p> -->

    <!-- Optional mailing address once a PO Box or registered agent is ready -->
    <!-- <p>Mail: Journal Foundation, PO Box 12345, City, ST 00000</p> -->
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .channel-list {
    margin-left: 0;
    padding-left: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .channel-list li {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--void-lighter);
  }

  .channel-note {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .channel-list li p:first-of-type {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .button-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    margin-right: var(--space-xs);
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--electric-blue);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--electric-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .button-link:hover,
  .button-link:focus {
    background: var(--electric-blue);
    color: var(--void);
  }

  .url-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin-left: var(--space-xs);
  }
</style>
